snippet.title: MareQuest: An Interactive Tail Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming to Steam September 15th! Wishlist today: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2391870/MareQuest_An_Interactive_Tail

Animation by @PearmareAnimation 

A terrible darkness threatens a world of overwhelmingly adorable mares. Can a new cute mare with amnesia save the world or will she lose more than her memories along the way? 

🔽 === ADDITIONAL LINKS === 🔽
Play the Original MareQuest FREE on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2184130/MareQuest/
Bandcamp OST Part 1: https://electrokaplosion.bandcamp.com/album/marequest-ost-part-i
Bandcamp OST Part 2: https://electrokaplosion.bandcamp.com/album/marequest-ost-part-ii
Twitter: https://twitter.com/EKaplosion
Discord: https://discord.gg/hueYuTRf6z
